<p><b>The universal implementation of international human rights treaties 
</b></p>
<p>41. At the same meeting, the Sub-Commission considered draft resolution 
A/HRC/Sub.1/58/L.7, sponsored by Mr. Alfredsson, Mr. Bengoa, Mr. B&#237;r&#243;, Mr. Chen Shiqiu, 
Mr. Cherif, Ms. Chung, Mr. Guiss&#233;, Ms. Hampson, Mr. Kartashkin, Ms. Koufa, Ms. Mbonu, 
