<p>163. The Sub-Commission considered agenda item 8 at its 23rd meeting, on 25 August 2006. 
</p>
<p>164. At that meeting, Mr. Cherif, Rapporteur of the Sub-Commission, presented the draft 
report on the work of its fifty-eighth session (A/HRC/Sub.1/58/L.10 and A/HRC/Sub.1/58/L.11 
and Add.1). 
</p>
<p>165. Statements in connection with the adoption of the report were made by 
Mr. Alfonso Mart&#237;nez, Mr. Bengoa, Mr. Decaux and Mr. Kartashkin. 
</p>
<p>166. At the same meeting, the Sub-Commission adopted the draft report ad referendum and 
decided to entrust the Rapporteur with its finalization. </p>

